summary: AN ORDINANCE designating the unnamed street fronting on Interstate 5, referred to on the State Freeway Plan as "Frontage Road - 75th - 80th" and "80th - 85th conn.", as Banner Way N.E. and designating the unnamed street, fronting on Interstate 5, referred to on the State Freeway Plan as "FR. 85th - 80th.," as Corliss Way North.
